These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, snooker
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, december
There are 2 different favourite colors: ivory, red
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, sports
1. the person watching action movies is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##8
2. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ivory##5
3. the person playing mah-jongg is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Game      | snooker     | mah-jongg      |
| Birthday          | december | october    |
| Color         | red   | ivory |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | sports      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
2 different games are played: domino, scrabble
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, woodworking
City: miami, edinburgh
There are 2 different favourite colors: grey, purple
1. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to miami##5
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is not to the right of the person traveling to miami##8
4. the person who likes grey is not the person who's hobby is woodworking##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Game    | domino        | scrabble    |
| Hobby       | filmmaking         | woodworking |
| City         | edinburgh | miami   |
| Color   | grey               | purple  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: video-games, cooking
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, metal
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, october
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, 7up
1. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the right of the person drinking 7up##8
3. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Hobby   | video-games       | cooking |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | metal    |
| Birthday   | may | october |
| Beverage           | lemonade        | 7up   |

