.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-20::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: rock-climbing, chess
2 different pets are kept: cat, ferret
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, ambient
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, scooter
1. the fan of gospel is not to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##8
2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |
| Hobby          | chess         | rock-climbing    |
| Pet           | cat | ferret   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | ambient    |
| Transport     | boat         | scooter |

 